              <h6><a name="protected_areas">PROTECTED AREAS</a></h6>
              <p>Protected areas are defined as terrestrial or marine areas that are recognised, dedicated and managed, through legal or other effective means, to achieve the long-term conservation of nature with associated ecosystem services and cultural values. This includes for example national parks and nature reserves.</p>
<p>
The Carbon and Biodiversity Calculator draws on the information in the World Database on Protected Areas.
</p>
